  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age: 2years or older and younger than 18 years

          -  Biopsy-proven Ig A Nephropathy

          -  Estimated GFR â‰¥ 90mL/min/m^2

          -  Mean urinary protein-creatinine ratio &gt; 0.3 g/g from three first-morning spot urine
